{
  "video_id": "ZnC_UBmeRxw",
  "title": "We train soldiers for war. Let's train them to come home, too | Hector Garcia",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12924.0,
      "end_time": 14477.0,
      "text": "Carlos,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14477.0,
      "end_time": 16054.0,
      "text": "the Vietnam vet Marine"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 16053.999999999998,
      "end_time": 20650.0,
      "text": "who volunteered for three tours and got shot up in every one."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20650.0,
      "end_time": 22776.0,
      "text": "In 1971, he was medically retired"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22776.0,
      "end_time": 25099.0,
      "text": "because he had so much shrapnel in his body"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25099.0,
      "end_time": 28279.0,
      "text": "that he was setting off metal detectors."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28279.0,
      "end_time": 31404.0,
      "text": "For the next 42 years, he suffered from nightmares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31404.0,
      "end_time": 33642.0,
      "text": "extreme anxiety in public,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33642.0,
      "end_time": 35677.0,
      "text": "isolation, depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35677.0,
      "end_time": 37605.0,
      "text": "He self-medicated with alcohol."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37605.0,
      "end_time": 40535.0,
      "text": "He was married and divorced three times."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40535.0,
      "end_time": 44129.0,
      "text": "Carlos had post-traumatic stress disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44129.0,
      "end_time": 47730.0,
      "text": "Now, I became a psychologist to help mitigate human suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47730.0,
      "end_time": 52241.0,
      "text": "and for the past 10 years, my target has been the suffering caused by PTSD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52241.0,
      "end_time": 55356.0,
      "text": "as experienced by veterans like Carlos."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55356.0,
      "end_time": 61161.0,
      "text": "Until recently, the science of PTSD just wasn&#39;t there."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61161.0,
      "end_time": 63561.0,
      "text": "And so, we didn&#39;t know what to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63561.0,
      "end_time": 65949.0,
      "text": "We put some veterans on heavy drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65949.0,
      "end_time": 68777.0,
      "text": "Others we hospitalized and gave generic group therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 68777.0,
      "end_time": 70899.0,
      "text": "and others still we simply said to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70899.0,
      "end_time": 75534.0,
      "text": "&quot;Just go home and try to forget about your experiences.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 75534.0,
      "end_time": 78901.0,
      "text": "More recently, we&#39;ve tried therapy dogs, wilderness retreats --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78901.0,
      "end_time": 81846.0,
      "text": "many things which may temporarily relieve stress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81846.0,
      "end_time": 86654.0,
      "text": "but which don&#39;t actually eliminate PTSD symptoms over the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 86654.0,
      "end_time": 88451.0,
      "text": "But things have changed."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88451.0,
      "end_time": 93631.0,
      "text": "And I am here to tell you that we can now eliminate PTSD,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93631.0,
      "end_time": 95482.0,
      "text": "not just manage the symptoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 95482.0,
      "end_time": 97054.0,
      "text": "and in huge numbers of veterans."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 97054.0,
      "end_time": 100056.0,
      "text": "Because new scientific research has been able to show,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100056.0,
      "end_time": 102458.0,
      "text": "objectively, repeatedly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 102458.0,
      "end_time": 105957.0,
      "text": "which treatments actually get rid of symptoms and which do not."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105957.0,
      "end_time": 107629.0,
      "text": "Now as it turns out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107629.0,
      "end_time": 112883.0,
      "text": "the best treatments for PTSD use many of the very same training principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112883.0,
      "end_time": 118227.0,
      "text": "that the military uses in preparing its trainees for war."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118227.0,
      "end_time": 120254.0,
      "text": "Now, making war --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120254.0,
      "end_time": 122993.0,
      "text": "this is something that we are good at."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122993.0,
      "end_time": 128006.0,
      "text": "We humans have been making war since before we were even fully human."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128006.0,
      "end_time": 131494.0,
      "text": "And since then, we have gone from using stone and sinew"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131494.0,
      "end_time": 136108.0,
      "text": "to developing the most sophisticated and devastating weapon systems imaginable."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136108.0,
      "end_time": 138467.0,
      "text": "And to enable our warriors to use these weapons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138467.0,
      "end_time": 140812.0,
      "text": "we employ the most cutting-edge training methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 140812.0,
      "end_time": 142898.0,
      "text": "We are good at making war."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 142898.0,
      "end_time": 146687.0,
      "text": "And we are good at training our warriors to fight."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 146687.0,
      "end_time": 150200.0,
      "text": "Yet, when we consider the experience of the modern-day combat veteran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 150200.0,
      "end_time": 153411.0,
      "text": "we begin to see that we have not been as good"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 153411.0,
      "end_time": 155447.0,
      "text": "at preparing them to come home."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155447.0,
      "end_time": 157731.0,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 157731.0,
      "end_time": 161029.0,
      "text": "Well, our ancestors lived immersed in conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 161029.0,
      "end_time": 164094.0,
      "text": "and they fought right where they lived."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 164094.0,
      "end_time": 167132.0,
      "text": "So until only very recently in our evolutionary history,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167132.0,
      "end_time": 170048.0,
      "text": "there was hardly a need to learn how to come home from war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170048.0,
      "end_time": 173377.0,
      "text": "because we never really did."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173377.0,
      "end_time": 174643.0,
      "text": "But thankfully, today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174643.0,
      "end_time": 177682.0,
      "text": "most of humanity lives in far more peaceful societies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177682.0,
      "end_time": 181685.0,
      "text": "and when there is conflict, we, especially in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 181685.0,
      "end_time": 185206.0,
      "text": "now have the technology to put our warriors through advanced training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185206.0,
      "end_time": 188047.0,
      "text": "drop them in to fight anywhere on the globe"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188047.0,
      "end_time": 189530.0,
      "text": "and when they&#39;re done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189530.0,
      "end_time": 192514.0,
      "text": "jet them back to peacetime suburbia."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192514.0,
      "end_time": 197064.0,
      "text": "But just imagine for a moment what this must feel like."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 197064.0,
      "end_time": 199108.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve spoken with veterans who&#39;ve told me"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 199108.0,
      "end_time": 202224.0,
      "text": "that one day they&#39;re in a brutal firefight in Afghanistan"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 202224.0,
      "end_time": 205867.0,
      "text": "where they saw carnage and death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 205867.0,
      "end_time": 208361.0,
      "text": "and just three days later, they found themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 208361.0,
      "end_time": 212405.0,
      "text": "toting an ice chest to their kid&#39;s soccer game."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 212405.0,
      "end_time": 215194.0,
      "text": "&quot;Mindfuck&quot; is the most common term."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215194.0,
      "end_time": 216632.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 216632.0,
      "end_time": 219775.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the most common term I&#39;ve heard to describe that experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 219775.0,
      "end_time": 221323.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s exactly what that is."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 221323.0,
      "end_time": 225336.0,
      "text": "Because while our warriors spend countless hours training for war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 225336.0,
      "end_time": 227253.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve only recently come to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 227253.0,
      "end_time": 231642.0,
      "text": "that many require training on how to return to civilian life."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 231642.0,
      "end_time": 235757.0,
      "text": "Now, like any training, the best PTSD treatments require repetition."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 235757.0,
      "end_time": 236932.0,
      "text": "In the military,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 236932.0,
      "end_time": 240196.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t simply hand trainees Mark-19 automatic grenade launchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 240196.0,
      "end_time": 243412.0,
      "text": "and say, &quot;Here&#39;s the trigger, here&#39;s some ammo and good luck.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 243412.0,
      "end_time": 248132.0,
      "text": "No. We train them, on the range and in specific contexts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 248132.0,
      "end_time": 249842.0,
      "text": "over and over and over"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 249842.0,
      "end_time": 252655.0,
      "text": "until lifting their weapon and engaging their target"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 252655.0,
      "end_time": 254515.0,
      "text": "is so engrained into muscle memory"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254515.0,
      "end_time": 256867.0,
      "text": "that it can be performed without even thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 256867.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260630.00000000003,
      "text": "even under the most stressful conditions you can imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 260630.0,
      "end_time": 263875.0,
      "text": "Now, the same holds for training-based treatments."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 263875.0,
      "end_time": 267230.0,
      "text": "The first of these treatments is cognitive therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 267230.0,
      "end_time": 271166.0,
      "text": "and this is a kind of mental recalibration."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 271166.0,
      "end_time": 272819.0,
      "text": "When veterans come home from war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 272819.0,
      "end_time": 275439.0,
      "text": "their way of mentally framing the world is calibrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 275439.0,
      "end_time": 278860.0,
      "text": "to an immensely more dangerous environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 278860.0,
      "end_time": 284040.0,
      "text": "So when you try to overlay that mind frame onto a peacetime environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 284040.0,
      "end_time": 285269.0,
      "text": "you get problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 285269.0,
      "end_time": 289748.0,
      "text": "You begin drowning in worries about dangers that aren&#39;t present."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289748.0,
      "end_time": 293935.0,
      "text": "You begin not trusting family or friends."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293935.0,
      "end_time": 298402.0,
      "text": "Which is not to say there are no dangers in civilian life; there are."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 298402.0,
      "end_time": 301118.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just that the probability of encountering them"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 301118.0,
      "end_time": 302412.0,
      "text": "compared to combat"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 302412.0,
      "end_time": 305675.0,
      "text": "is astronomically lower."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 305675.0,
      "end_time": 308839.0,
      "text": "So we never advise veterans to turn off caution completely."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 308839.0,
      "end_time": 311247.0,
      "text": "We do train them, however, to adjust caution"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 311247.0,
      "end_time": 313685.0,
      "text": "according to where they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 313685.0,
      "end_time": 316194.0,
      "text": "If you find yourself in a bad neighborhood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 316194.0,
      "end_time": 317878.0,
      "text": "you turn it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 317878.0,
      "end_time": 319551.0,
      "text": "Out to dinner with family?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 319551.0,
      "end_time": 321975.0,
      "text": "You turn it way down."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 321975.0,
      "end_time": 325271.0,
      "text": "We train veterans to be fiercely rational,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 325271.0,
      "end_time": 328849.0,
      "text": "to systematically gauge the actual statistical probability"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 328849.0,
      "end_time": 333460.0,
      "text": "of encountering, say, an IED here in peacetime America."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 333460.0,
      "end_time": 339193.0,
      "text": "With enough practice, those recalibrations stick."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 339193.0,
      "end_time": 341531.0,
      "text": "The next of these treatments is exposure therapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 341531.0,
      "end_time": 344453.0,
      "text": "and this is a kind of field training,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 344453.0,
      "end_time": 347974.0,
      "text": "and the fastest of the proven effective treatments out there."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 347974.0,
      "end_time": 349555.0,
      "text": "You remember Carlos?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 349555.0,
      "end_time": 351869.0,
      "text": "This was the treatment that he chose."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 351869.0,
      "end_time": 354333.0,
      "text": "And so we started off by giving him exercises,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 354333.0,
      "end_time": 355663.0,
      "text": "for him, challenging ones:"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 355663.0,
      "end_time": 357633.0,
      "text": "going to a grocery store,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357633.0,
      "end_time": 360282.0,
      "text": "going to a shopping mall, going to a restaurant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 360282.0,
      "end_time": 363214.0,
      "text": "sitting with his back to the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 363214.0,
      "end_time": 365032.0,
      "text": "And, critically --"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 365032.0,
      "end_time": 367791.0,
      "text": "staying in these environments."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367791.0,
      "end_time": 369525.0,
      "text": "Now, at first he was very anxious."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369525.0,
      "end_time": 372041.0,
      "text": "He wanted to sit where he could scan the room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 372041.0,
      "end_time": 373990.0,
      "text": "where he could plan escape routes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 373990.0,
      "end_time": 377041.0,
      "text": "where he could get his hands on a makeshift weapon."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 377041.0,
      "end_time": 380390.0,
      "text": "And he wanted to leave, but he didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 380390.0,
      "end_time": 383285.0,
      "text": "He remembered his training in the Marine Corps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 383285.0,
      "end_time": 385530.0,
      "text": "and he pushed through his discomfort."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 385530.0,
      "end_time": 388746.0,
      "text": "And every time he did this, his anxiety ratcheted down a little bit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 388746.0,
      "end_time": 391529.0,
      "text": "and then a little bit more and then a little bit more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391529.0,
      "end_time": 392867.0,
      "text": "until in the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 392867.0,
      "end_time": 398785.0,
      "text": "he had effectively relearned how to sit in a public space"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 398785.0,
      "end_time": 401704.0,
      "text": "and just enjoy himself."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 401704.0,
      "end_time": 405046.0,
      "text": "He also listened to recordings of his combat experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 405046.0,
      "end_time": 407706.0,
      "text": "over and over and over."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 407706.0,
      "end_time": 412419.0,
      "text": "He listened until those memories no longer generated any anxiety."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 412419.0,
      "end_time": 415005.0,
      "text": "He processed his memories so much"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 415005.0,
      "end_time": 418258.0,
      "text": "that his brain no longer needed to return to those experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 418258.0,
      "end_time": 420400.0,
      "text": "in his sleep."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 420400.0,
      "end_time": 423977.0,
      "text": "And when I spoke with him a year after treatment had finished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 423977.0,
      "end_time": 425372.0,
      "text": "he told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 425372.0,
      "end_time": 430472.0,
      "text": "&quot;Doc, this is the first time in 43 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 430472.0,
      "end_time": 433412.0,
      "text": "that I haven&#39;t had nightmares.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 433412.0,
      "end_time": 438087.0,
      "text": "Now, this is different than erasing a memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 438087.0,
      "end_time": 441106.0,
      "text": "Veterans will always remember their traumatic experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 441106.0,
      "end_time": 442787.0,
      "text": "but with enough practice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 442787.0,
      "end_time": 448379.0,
      "text": "those memories are no longer as raw or as painful as they once were."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 448379.0,
      "end_time": 451964.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t feel emotionally like they just happened yesterday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 451964.0,
      "end_time": 457985.0,
      "text": "and that is an immensely better place to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 457985.0,
      "end_time": 459677.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s often difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 459677.0,
      "end_time": 464117.0,
      "text": "And, like any training, it may not work for everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 464117.0,
      "end_time": 465931.0,
      "text": "And there are trust issues."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 465931.0,
      "end_time": 467237.0,
      "text": "Sometimes I&#39;m asked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 467237.0,
      "end_time": 469915.0,
      "text": "&quot;If you haven&#39;t been there, Doc, how can you help me?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 469915.0,
      "end_time": 472244.0,
      "text": "Which is understandable."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 472244.0,
      "end_time": 476639.0,
      "text": "But at the point of returning to civilian life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 476639.0,
      "end_time": 479985.0,
      "text": "you do not require somebody who&#39;s been there."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 479985.0,
      "end_time": 483125.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t require training for operations on the battlefield;"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 483125.0,
      "end_time": 490626.0,
      "text": "you require training on how to come home."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 490626.0,
      "end_time": 493336.0,
      "text": "For the past 10 years of my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 493336.0,
      "end_time": 496108.0,
      "text": "I have been exposed to detailed accounts"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 496108.0,
      "end_time": 498732.0,
      "text": "of the worst experiences that you can imagine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 498732.0,
      "end_time": 499985.0,
      "text": "daily."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 499985.0,
      "end_time": 502107.0,
      "text": "And it hasn&#39;t always been easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 502107.0,
      "end_time": 505496.0,
      "text": "There have been times where I have just felt my heart break"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 505496.0,
      "end_time": 508150.0,
      "text": "or that I&#39;ve absorbed too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 508150.0,
      "end_time": 511497.0,
      "text": "But these training-based treatments work so well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 511497.0,
      "end_time": 514603.0,
      "text": "that whatever this work takes out of me, it puts back even more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 514602.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518753.99999999994,
      "text": "because I see people get better."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 518754.0,
      "end_time": 522656.0,
      "text": "I see people&#39;s lives transform."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 522655.99999999994,
      "end_time": 526018.0,
      "text": "Carlos can now enjoy outings with his grandchildren,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 526018.0,
      "end_time": 529638.0,
      "text": "which is something he couldn&#39;t even do with his own children."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 529638.0,
      "end_time": 533648.0,
      "text": "And what&#39;s amazing to me is that after 43 years of suffering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 533648.0,
      "end_time": 538001.0,
      "text": "it only took him 10 weeks of intense training to get his life back."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 538001.0,
      "end_time": 540333.0,
      "text": "And when I spoke with him, he told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 540333.0,
      "end_time": 545088.0,
      "text": "&quot;I know that I can&#39;t get those years back."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 545088.0,
      "end_time": 550021.0,
      "text": "But at least now, whatever days that I have left on this Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 550021.0,
      "end_time": 553114.0,
      "text": "I can live them in peace.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 553114.0,
      "end_time": 556610.0,
      "text": "He also said, &quot;I hope that these younger veterans don&#39;t wait"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 556610.0,
      "end_time": 558588.0,
      "text": "to get the help they need.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 558588.0,
      "end_time": 561020.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s my hope, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 561020.0,
      "end_time": 563003.0,
      "text": "Because ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 563003.0,
      "end_time": 565383.0,
      "text": "this life is short,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 565383.0,
      "end_time": 568579.0,
      "text": "and if you are fortunate enough to have survived war"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 568579.0,
      "end_time": 570683.0,
      "text": "or any kind of traumatic experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 570683.0,
      "end_time": 574629.0,
      "text": "you owe it to yourself to live your life well."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 574629.0,
      "end_time": 577294.0,
      "text": "And you shouldn&#39;t wait to get the training you need"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 577294.0,
      "end_time": 580663.0,
      "text": "to make that happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 580663.0,
      "end_time": 586883.0,
      "text": "Now, the best way of ending human suffering caused by war"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 586883.0,
      "end_time": 589422.0,
      "text": "is to never go to war."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 589422.0,
      "end_time": 592157.0,
      "text": "But we are just not there yet as a species."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 592157.0,
      "end_time": 593441.0,
      "text": "Until we are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 593441.0,
      "end_time": 598698.0,
      "text": "the mental suffering that we create in our sons and in our daughters"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 598698.0,
      "end_time": 600682.0,
      "text": "when we send them off to fight"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 600682.0,
      "end_time": 603675.0,
      "text": "can be alleviated."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 603675.0,
      "end_time": 609785.0,
      "text": "But we must ensure that the science, the energy level, the value"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 609785.0,
      "end_time": 613516.0,
      "text": "that we place on sending them off to war"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 613516.0,
      "end_time": 615450.0,
      "text": "is at the very least mirrored"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 615450.0,
      "end_time": 619868.0,
      "text": "in how well we prepare them to come back home to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 619868.0,
      "end_time": 622186.0,
      "text": "This much, we owe them."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 622186.0,
      "end_time": 623393.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 623393.0,
      "end_time": 633393.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}